    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized valve timing across the rev range. The power is managed by a desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Mechanical integrity is prioritized, with the critical rod bearing service completed and the rear subframe reinforced to prevent common chassis fatigue. The suspension remains taut, utilizing its original MacPherson strut and multi-link geometry for exceptional lateral grip. An honest, driver-focused example that balances raw performance with documented mechanical longevity.",
